data.description: Welcome home to a fantastic neighborhood in Oakland Park, featuring a beautiful single family home in the heart of Fort Lauderdale, offering a mix of suburban comfort and urban conveniences.  Turnkey, all new appliances, washer/dryer, updated kitchen, new electrical panels, impact glass/shutters for complete hurricane protection, new wifi irrigation system, smart lock and ring security system. Each of the three bedrooms features an en suite bath.  Perfect primary home, investment property or short term-rental!This home also features a large pavered backyard patio with a free-standing gazebo for relaxing or entertaining, an enclosed sun room, and a completely fenced, private yard with room for a pool. Home also features a private entry to the primary bedroom suite.
